      • save

        public void save()
        Description copied from interface: User
        Saves this User to the designed form of storage. This method will run asynchronously to ensure that it does not cause hesitation in the main thread. This means that saving very often causes no issues except traffic either to the database or the file system itself. Regardless, it should still be used sparingly to ensure as much efficiency as possible.
